				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Jingak-Hyesim/Ba-ti%C3%AAu/poem-8-yqjeSJU7z2eWH2hZgpXQ">Ba tiêu - 芭蕉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Jingak-Hyesim/author-RGxtMe1sV6AuAbjteu9Sdg">Jingak Hyesim</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Quan-H%C3%A1n-Khanh/B%C3%ADch-ng%E1%BB%8Dc-ti%C3%AAu-k%E1%BB%B3-04/poem-GLzqIGvVnoBURna-hgD_jw">Bích ngọc tiêu kỳ 04 - 碧玉簫其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Quan-H%C3%A1n-Khanh/author-YR1JO8YsFFO7R_h7lgqsNQ">Quan Hán Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/B%E1%BB%93-t%C3%A1t-man-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-RTo6Tb5K3fIK1n0GvUsHmA">Bồ tát man kỳ 4 - 菩薩蠻其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/author-VkIfi7DKP2f1cM8JZZP8yA">Ôn Đình Quân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/D%E1%BA%A1-quy/poem-rCpLS4pHYsVrJjKIhfTnOg">Dạ quy - 夜歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/%C4%90%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BA%A5t-c%E1%BA%A3nh-Tr%C3%B9ng-minh-vi%E1%BB%85n-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-V-iugDpXO8fyh7Gh59sB-g">Đệ nhất cảnh - Trùng minh viễn chiếu - 第一景－重明遠照</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-nC6naBeYFtCN3Ft17XDeJw">Thiệu Trị hoàng đế</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-K%E1%BA%BF-M%C3%B4n-kh%C3%A1n-%C4%91%C4%83ng/poem-EH-PJ-AY05o7OY2RhNj52A">Đồng Trương Tương Kế Môn khán đăng - 同張將薊門看燈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/author-ep8IiRc7UH2qX75S-LVnLw">Mạnh Hạo Nhiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/S%C6%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-v